DeleteEarthObservationJob.name: DeleteEarthObservationJob
DeleteEarthObservationJob.description: Grants permission to the DeleteEarthObservationJob operation which deletes an existing earth observation job

DeleteVectorEnrichmentJob.name: DeleteVectorEnrichmentJob
DeleteVectorEnrichmentJob.description: Grants permission to the DeleteVectorEnrichmentJob operation which deletes an existing vector enrichment job

ExportEarthObservationJob.name: ExportEarthObservationJob
ExportEarthObservationJob.description: Grants permission to copy results of an earth observation job to an S3 location

ExportVectorEnrichmentJob.name: ExportVectorEnrichmentJob
ExportVectorEnrichmentJob.description: Grants permission to copy results of an VectorEnrichmentJob to an S3 location

GetEarthObservationJob.name: GetEarthObservationJob
GetEarthObservationJob.description: Grants permission to return details about the earth observation job

GetRasterDataCollection.name: GetRasterDataCollection
GetRasterDataCollection.description: Grants permission to return details about the raster data collection

GetTile.name: GetTile
GetTile.description: Grants permission to get the tile of an earth observation job

GetVectorEnrichmentJob.name: GetVectorEnrichmentJob
GetVectorEnrichmentJob.description: Grants permission to return details about the vector enrichment job

ListEarthObservationJobs.name: ListEarthObservationJobs
ListEarthObservationJobs.description: Grants permission to return an array of earth observation jobs associated with the current account

ListRasterDataCollections.name: ListRasterDataCollections
ListRasterDataCollections.description: Grants permission to return an array of aster data collections associated with the given model name

ListTagsForResource.name: ListTagsForResource
ListTagsForResource.description: Grants permission to lists tag for an SageMaker Geospatial resource

ListVectorEnrichmentJobs.name: ListVectorEnrichmentJobs
ListVectorEnrichmentJobs.description: Grants permission to return an array of vector enrichment jobs associated with the current account

SearchRasterDataCollection.name: SearchRasterDataCollection
SearchRasterDataCollection.description: Grants permission to query raster data collections

StartEarthObservationJob.name: StartEarthObservationJob
StartEarthObservationJob.description: Grants permission to the StartEarthObservationJob operation which starts a new earth observation job to your account

StartVectorEnrichmentJob.name: StartVectorEnrichmentJob
StartVectorEnrichmentJob.description: Grants permission to the StartVectorEnrichmentJob operation which starts a new vector enrichment job to your account

StopEarthObservationJob.name: StopEarthObservationJob
StopEarthObservationJob.description: Grants permission to the StopEarthObservationJob operation which stops an existing earth observation job

StopVectorEnrichmentJob.name: StopVectorEnrichmentJob
StopVectorEnrichmentJob.description: Grants permission to the StopVectorEnrichmentJob operation which stops an existing vector enrichment job

TagResource.name: TagResource
TagResource.description: Grants permission to tag an SageMaker Geospatial resource

UntagResource.name: UntagResource
UntagResource.description: Grants permission to untag an SageMaker Geospatial resource
